# GoldMoodAstro Mobile — environment template
# Lokal dev için: kopyalayıp .env olarak kaydedin (gitignore'lı).
# Production build'lerinde eas.json profillerindeki env değerleri kullanılır.

# API base URL (backend Fastify prefix'i: /api)
# Simulator: http://localhost:8094/api
# Gerçek cihaz (telefondan PC'ye): http://<bilgisayar-IP>:8094/api
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8094/api
EXPO_PUBLIC_APP_NAME=GoldMoodAstro
EXPO_PUBLIC_PUBLIC_URL=https://goldmoodastro.com
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPPORT_EMAIL=destek@goldmoodastro.com
EXPO_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=http://localhost:3000

# ─── IAP Product IDs ──────────────────────────────────────
EXPO_PUBLIC_IAP_PRODUCT_MONTHLY_IOS=com.goldmoodastro.app.monthly
EXPO_PUBLIC_IAP_PRODUCT_YEARLY_IOS=com.goldmoodastro.app.yearly
EXPO_PUBLIC_IAP_PRODUCT_MONTHLY_ANDROID=com.goldmoodastro.app.monthly
EXPO_PUBLIC_IAP_PRODUCT_YEARLY_ANDROID=com.goldmoodastro.app.yearly
EXPO_PUBLIC_IAP_PRODUCT_MONTHLY=
EXPO_PUBLIC_IAP_PRODUCT_YEARLY=
